\par 
\par The angry man lowered the briefcase, swallowed.
\par 
\par "You can go out and get in your car and leave Santaroga," Marden said.  "Now.  And don't come back.  We'll be watching for you, and we'll run you in if we ever catch you in the valley again."
\par 
