A corner of a wheeled tray appeared.  Dishes clattered.  The door swung wider.
\par 
\par Jenny appeared in the doorway pushing the tray.  Dasein stared at her in the mirror, his hands frozen at the tie.  She wore a red dress, her long black hair caught in a matching bandeaux.  
