\par "Odd alertness about the natives.  Sharpness of attitude toward each other and outsiders.
\par 
\par "Question local use of Jaspers products.  Why won't the cheese travel?  What's the reason for the decided local preference?  It tastes different than what I bought outside.  What about aftertaste?  Subjective?  What relationship to the beer?
\par 
\par "Investigate use of Jaspers as a label.  Adjective?"
\par 
\par Something big was moving through the trees on the hill beyond the Co-op.  The movement caught Dasein's attention.  He studied it a moment.  Too many trees intervened to permit a clear look.
\par 
