't realize how much we want you to be one of us.  So I brought you some of my sour cream stew -- plenty of Jaspers."
\par 
\par She thrust the dish at him.
\par 
\par Dasein took it.  Smooth, warm china under his hands.  He fought down an unreasonable impulse to drop the dish and smash it.  He was afraid suddenly.  Perspiration made his palms slippery against the dish.
