\par 
\par "Oh, my God!  The paint bleach
," she said.  She dropped the dish, whirled away, dashed to the car before Dasein could stop her.  The Chevrolet leaped to life, turned in a whirl of sand and roared out the track to the highway.  It made a skidding turn onto the highway, raced back towar
d town.
\par 
