\par 
\par "Come along," Piaget said.  "I'll show you our school."
\par 
\par Dasein shook his head.  What would it be in there?  An accidental push against broken glass?  A child with a knife?
\par 
\par "I'm . . . I have to think," Dasein said.
\par 
\par "Are you sure?"  Piaget's words dropped on the air like a challenge.
\par 
