\par 
\par "The ones who hired me," Dasein said, "they're men who believe . . ."
\par 
\par "Men!" Piaget sneered.  "Out there . . ."  He pointed beyond the hills which enclosed the valley.  " . . . they're destroying their environment.  In the process, they're becoming not-m
