\par 
\par Dasein looked at the greenhouses.
\par 
\par "Yes," Piaget said.  "Look here.  That is where we domesticate the human animal."
\par 
\par With a shock of awareness, Dasein realized he had heard too much ever to be allowed out of the valley.  They had passed a point of no return with him.  In h
