\par 
\par The garage doors were open.  Dasein nosed the truck insid
e, stopped, climbed out.  There was a steady sound of work all around -- clanging of metal, machinery humming.  Lines of cars had been angled toward benches down both sides of the garage.  Lights glared down on the benches.
\par 
