\par 
\par Dasein studied the can:  shiny, a glistening label.
\par 
\par "Beans with meat sauce and beef," read the yellow letters.
\par 
\par Dasein ignored the lure of the aroma from the can, looked in the box.  He tried to remember whether the can had given off the characteristic hiss of a vacuum seal breaking as it had been opened -- couldn't remember.
